dct_title_s: Carte géographique, statistique et historique du New-Jersey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. From: Atlas géographique, historique et chronologique des deux Amériques ... Paris : J. Carez, [1825]. Prime meridians: Washington and Paris. Includes text in French on New Jersey geology, population, governors and history, with title: New-Jersey. J.A.C. Buchon published a French edition of Carey and Lea's American atlas of 1822; cf. Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers.
dct_publisher_sm: [Paris] : Fonderie et imprimerie de J. Carez, [1825]
